text: Towson Run is a tributary of Jones Falls, a stream in Baltimore County, Maryland, in the United States. The stream runs north through Sheppard Pratt and Towson University, near the communities of Rodgers Forge and Armagh Village. ==Geology== The type locality of the Baltimore Gneiss outcrops along Towson Run from Bellona Avenue to Towsontown Boulevard. ==References== Category:Rivers of Maryland Category:Rivers of Baltimore County, Maryland
title: Towson Run
